OL,9,     Gaircraft.
OL,10,G1055FFour in a Bed
OL,11,     GNewly engaged couple Rosie and
OL,12,     GDexter welcome their rivals to
OL,13,     Gthe Bae Abermaw Hotel in
OL,14,     GBarmouth, Wales. The guests are
OL,15,     Gwowed by the views but surprised
OL,16,     Gby their hosts' romantic
OL,17,     Grevelations.
