OL,4,G1230FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GNici and Ros host at The Cross
OL,6,     GKeys Hotel in Saffron Walden,
OL,7,     GEssex. Their guests lap up the
OL,8,     Gluxury, but Tracy finds a mark on
OL,9,     Gher towel, and tensions threaten
OL,10,     Gto boil over at dinner.
OL,11,G1615FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GThe first visit is to Harrogate,
OL,13,     Gwhere management team 'Clarkey'
OL,14,     Gand Katie help to run the 64-
OL,15,     Gbedroom White Hart Hotel. The
OL,16,     Gextra charge for posh coffee at
OL,17,     Gbreakfast causes a stir.
