OL,8,     GBeacons. The guests gush over
OL,9,     Gtheir new friendships, but Vicky
OL,10,     Gdoesn't seem to share the
OL,11,     Gsentiment.
OL,12,G1820FFour in a Bed
OL,13,     GIt's the final day of the
OL,14,     Gcompetition and the B&Bers meet
OL,15,     Gfor the last time to settle some
OL,16,     Gscores. There's anger as well as
OL,17,     Gtears of joy when the winner is
OL,18,     Grevealed.
